# Technical Stack

- Next.js for the frontend framework
- pnpm as the package manager
- Supabase for user authentication and database
- @balldontlie/sdk for sports data integration
- TypeScript for all code files
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- React Query for data fetching
- Vercel for hosting and deployment
- ESLint + Prettier for code quality
- Jest for unit testing
- App Router for Next.js routing
- Server components for data-heavy operations
- Client components for interactive UI elements
- Edge functions for API routes
- Row-Level Security for Supabase tables